This is a unittest framework for C++.

Prerequisites:
Later GCC (4.7.0≤) or Clang (3.1≤)
Boost C++ Libraries (use Boost.Fusion)

Build:
git clone git://github.com/dechimal/atto-test.git
cd atto-test
echo 'BOOST_INCLUDE := /path/to/boost' >Makefile.config
make

Installation:
cp -r include/atto-test /path/to/include
cp src/libattotest.so /path/to/lib

Usage:
See 10-test.cpp and Makefile under test/

This library uses some C++11's new features. So require to compile tests as C++11.
